---
const CHECKS = [
  '数日経っても、飽きずに食べてくれるか',
  'お腹の調子は、安定しているか',
  '今のフードから、スムーズに切り替えられるか',
  '毛艶や元気さに、変化があるか',
];
---

<div class="section" style="background:#fefbf4" data-section="why" data-section-order="6">
  <div class="screen-wrapper">
    <div class="why screen">
      <div class="why__header">
        <div class="why__label">WHY 2kg</div>
        <h1 class="why__title">2kgあるから、<br />相性が見えてくる。</h1>
      </div>

      <p class="why__lead">
        ひと口、ふた口、食べてくれた。<br />
        それだけでは、本当に合うかは分かりません。<br />
        愛犬との相性は、もう少し先に見えてきます。
      </p>

      <ul class="why__checks">
        {CHECKS.map((text) => (
          <li class="why__check-item">
            <span class="why__check-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
                <path d="M2.5 7.2L5.5 10.2L11.5 4.2" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="why__check-text">{text}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>

      <p class="why__body">
        だから私たちは、2kgでお試しいただけるようにしました。<br />
        ゆっくり、1〜2週間かけて切り替えながら、<br />
        愛犬の様子を見てあげてください。
      </p>

      <img class="why__image" src="/img/why2kg.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .section {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
    height: 100dvh;
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    padding-bottom: 60px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
  }

  .screen-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .why {
    position: relative;
    width: 440px !important;
    height: 959px !important;
    overflow: hidden !important;
    background-color: var(--background-02);
    will-change: transform;
  }

  /* Header */
  .why__header {
    position: absolute;
    top: 70px;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .why__label {
    color: var(--orange);
    font-size: var(--font-size-s);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.70px;
  }

  .why__title {
    margin: 8px 0 0;
    color: var(--brown-title-text);
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.80px;
    line-height: 52px;
  }

  /* Lead text */
  .why__lead {
    position: absolute;
    top: 215px;
    left: 20px;
    width: 400px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--eerie-black);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.07px;
    line-height: 26px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Checks (white card) */
  .why__checks {
    position: absolute;
    top: 310px;
    left: 20px;
    width: 400px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 13px 20px;
    list-style: none;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 5px #0000000d;
  }

  .why__check-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 9px 0;
  }

  .why__check-item + .why__check-item {
    border-top: 1px dashed #e8e8e8;
  }

  .why__check-icon {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background-color: var(--green);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .why__check-text {
    flex: 1;
    color: var(--eerie-black);
    font-size: 14.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    line-height: 22px;
  }

  /* Body text */
  .why__body {
    position: absolute;
    top: 525px;
    left: 20px;
    width: 400px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--eerie-black);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.07px;
    line-height: 26px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Dog image */
  .why__image {
    position: absolute;
    top: 597px;
    left: calc(50% - 121px);
    width: 242px;
    height: 242px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
</style>
